<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.11">
<l>māliruñ cōlaiyeṉṉum malaiyaiyuṭai yamalaiyai</l>
<l>nāliru mūrttitaṉṉai nālvētaka ṭalamutai</l>
<l>mēliruṅ kaṟpakattai vētāntavi ḻupporuḷil</l>
<l>mēlirun taviḷakkai viṭṭucittaṉ virittaṉavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain [like Lord] who has [as his place]</l>
<l rend="indent">the mountain called Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l>he with the four eminent forms,</l>
<l>the nectar of the ocean of the four Vedas</l>
<l>the heavenly Kaṟpaka tree</l>
<l>the heavenly light on the highest meaning of the Vedānta –</l>
<l rend="indent">these have been expounded by Viṭṭucittaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
